CHANGES IN VERSION 1.1.0
------------------------

USER VISIBLE CHANGES

    o knitr chunk_opts error=FALSE by default, so failures during
    vignette processing are signaled to R CMD build and R CMD check

    o Name-mangle \comment mark-up to avoid conflicts with other LaTeX
    styles

    o Introduce \bioctitle to allow for full and short (header) titles

CHANGES IN VERSION 1.0.0
------------------------

USER VISIBLE CHANGES

    o Rename \Rpkg{} as \CRANpkg{} to reflect functionality

BUG FIXES

    o avoid option conflict with \usepackage{colors}
